<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header p {
            font-size: 45px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .content h2 {
            font-size: 35px;
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content .welcome-text {
            font-size: 30px;
            color: #666666;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .content .details {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #666666;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: crimson;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <p>Your Tour Guide</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <img src="https://your-image-link.com/tour-image.jpg" alt="image"/>
            <p>Hello <%=name%>,</p>
            <h2>Booking Confirmation</h2>
            <p class="welcome-text">Your booking has been confirmed!</p>
            <p class="details">
                Thank you for booking with Your Tour Guide. Your trip details are as follows:
                <br>
                <strong>Tour:</strong> <%=tourName%><br>
                <strong>Date:</strong> <%=bookingDate%><br>
                <strong>Number of Guests:</strong> <%=numGuests%><br>
                <strong>Total Price:</strong> <%=totalPrice%><br>
                <br>
                We look forward to having you on board. If you have any questions or need further assistance, please feel free to contact us. Happy travels!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <a href="#">View Booking</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
